In US there was about 16,438 car crashes per day in 2020 , due to innattention of the driver, or light and road condition , or sometimes it could be caused due tu the weather , 
many people die everyday because of car accidents , so here a problem is setted of , if we suppose that the severity of a car accident can be known based on light and road conditio
and the weather , then we will be able to predict how severity a car accident may be ,based on the conditions that we have , and then we could be able to protect the driver from 
this accident by averting him , and we eill minimise the number of car accidents per day.
